  <name>VALHALLA</name>
  <developer id="net.valhalla">
    <name>VALHALLA Team</name>
  </developer>
  <summary>Arena shooter with a touch of Norse mythology</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      VALHALLA is an open-source FPS that combines modern casual gameplay with a touch of old-school charm, set within a sci-fi reimagining of Norse mythology.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Fast paced and snappy gameplay: hop into the Valhalla Corporation's testing arenas - for science!</li>
      <li>Blow the hell out of the opposition with 7 main weapons, complete with alternative firing modes</li>
      <li>Get 6 nasty power-ups to unleash against your unsuspecting opponents</li>
      <li>Test your reflexes on various situations with 9 gamemodes and 9 mutators, offering both competitive and casual games</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
